  "commentary": "With SPX at 6815.31 sitting above the 6798 flip in a PIN regime, dealers are long gamma and will sell into this recent strength while providing support on any dip toward 6810. The massive +6.2B gamma wall at 6810 creates a strong magnetic pull just below current levels, while the thick positive gamma structure through 6900-7000 will act as speed bumps on any rally attempt. Watch for mean reversion back toward 6810 given the -1.1% move and dealers' stabilizing flow profile.\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pulled back down toward 6810 with dealers capping upside momentum.",
